It was a lot of fun! You wanna grab a drink?
Dude, how old are you? Can I see your ID?
I said the Lady is thirsty. Two specials, please.
Yeah, uh... I’ve gotten some extra benefits from my deal.
Not sure why, but Lilith seems to be...
Just be careful, none of them have
So, you ever use that power on me?
I... Don’t think so? I don’t know, honestly. I kinda use it
when I feel like I need to, like it’s second nature but...
I dunno, I don’t think I ever needed it with you.
Well, that’s a relief. It took a lot for me to come out
tonight, I’m... I’m glad it was my decision in the end.
Of course, I don’t like to think of it as me forcing anyone
to do anything, just kinda... I dunno, nudging them towards
what they wanted to do anyways.
Here you go, two specials. Enjoy!
Sorry to intrude, but Miss... I would never
forgive myself if I didn’t talk to you.
You have to be the most stunningly beautiful woman to ever
enter this club, and I don’t make that comment freely.
Emperor. I own the Sway, and I assure you sir, I’m not
trying to put any moves on your girl.
I’m a collector of talent, though, and I’d be remiss to
let a specimen such as yourself walk out of here, my lady.
Are... Are you trying to sell me something or..?
No no, just the opposite. I’d like
to hire you, if you’re available.
The way you moved earlier was quite a sight. I think
you would do great dancing above the crowd, don’t you?
It’s your life, Angie. Maybe it’s time you start taking
control over it again. You are a great dancer, and working
here would get you back in shape really quickly...
Have you ever danced for a crowd before?
Maybe just try it tonight - just once, please.
Whatever you want to do, Angie, I’m here...
Okay, but... But just one dance!
Welcome to the dance floor, the lovely Angel - Angelina!
That was so fun! Did you see me?!
You’re a natural! So, what do you think - will you take
the job? I can pay you $200 a night as a start, none of
my girls make that. Please, I need you at my club...
Oh gosh, am I really worth that much?
That’s like four grand a month, you gotta take that, right?
I... YES! I’ll take the job!
Fantastic! Here’s my contact info, come back tomorrow night
and we can get you set up. It was nice meeting you, my dear.
Thank you! Thank you so much for this opportunity!
Yeah, thanks man. You really did her a solid.
Nothing! Back to work - music to play,
drinks to sell, money to make!
This has been a really amazing night, \N[001]. Thank you.
It’s what you deserve, and a lot more.
I just wanted you to see that too.
Did you maybe want to... Go back to my place?
Hey Angie! Lookin' good! You having fun working here?
Oh, it's been great! All the girls are super nice so
far, I just get to dance and have fun all night and
wanted to take a break sometime..?
